#: C/system-admin-guide.xml:514(para)
msgid "Below are listed some of the options that you can use with the <command>mateconftool-2</command> command. For detailed command line options, please see <ulink url=\"man:mateconftool-2(1)\">man:mateconftool-2(1)</ulink>."
